WEBVTT

00:11.906 --> 00:13.876
Man, why am I so sleepy?

00:14.150 --> 00:16.717
Dude, we've been up
for like seven days.

00:17.819 --> 00:18.757
For real-sies?

00:19.044 --> 00:20.306
Yeah, for real-sies!

00:21.323 --> 00:26.285
Remember? First, we saved the Slime
Princess from the Ghost-Ship Vortex.

00:27.711 --> 00:29.879
And then we slayed that fire dragon.

00:31.442 --> 00:32.917
And that took a couple of days.

00:33.083 --> 00:34.965
Then we went to LSP's quinceañera.

00:35.090 --> 00:37.396
Oh, no way. You guys made it!

00:37.765 --> 00:40.040
Helped Peppermint Butler
with his Goblin problem.

00:40.334 --> 00:43.728
I swear that i found it like this.
I don't know what happened.

00:43.853 --> 00:45.636
We'll take care of it,
Peppermint Butler.

00:46.034 --> 00:49.189
Saved Wildberry Princess
from the Ice King.

00:49.314 --> 00:51.316
I just wanna be happy!

00:51.709 --> 00:54.477
- Then, we captured that Bandito.
- Thanks, you guys.

00:54.643 --> 00:55.896
Saved the house...

00:56.183 --> 00:57.197
Thanks, you guys.

00:57.465 --> 00:58.865
And fed that duck.

01:02.174 --> 01:03.424
We've had a busy week.

01:03.694 --> 01:05.197
I'm exhausted. But happy!

01:06.722 --> 01:08.797
- Good night, buddy.
- Good night!

01:09.219 --> 01:11.682
That's right, Finn.
Adventure'til you drop.

01:13.000 --> 01:19.074
